OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wed 27 May to Fri 5 Jun
OL,6,FWith high pressure expected to remain
OL,7,Fin place for much of the UK, fine
OL,8,Fweather and light winds are likely to
OL,9,Fcontinue for most places. Although
OL,10,Fperhaps not as warm as the start of
OL,11,Fthe week, temperatures will still be
OL,12,Fwarm or very warm inland, but it will
OL,13,Ffeel cooler near the coast, especially
OL,14,Fwith an onshore breeze. Some patchy
OL,15,Frain may affect the far northwest at
OL,16,Ftimes, with perhaps a few showers in
OL,17,Fthe far south.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
